title: Deposit Interest Rate in Russia
description: Deposit Interest Rate in Russia increased to 5.55 percent in September from 5.06 percent in August of 2022. Deposit Interest Rate in Russia averaged 8.05 percent from 1995 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 101.96 percent in December of 1995 and a record low of 3.21 percent in February of 2021. The Deposit Interest Rate in Russia refers to average deposit rate paid by commercial banks to individuals. This page includes a chart with historical data for Deposit Interest Rate in Russia.
author: Central Bank of Russia
